      "title": "MRP for 43 Medical Devices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Minister of Health Keheliya Rambukwella has issued an Extraordinary Gazette amending the Maximum Retail Prices of 43 medical equipment and pharmaceutical drugs.",
        "As per the gazette, a revised price has been introduced for several types of Intraocular Lenses.",
        "The Health Minister has also imposed a new MRP for Glucometers and Pulse Oximeters.",
        "Promptly Resolve Fuel, Gas and Paddy Issues \u2013 Senior Advisor to the President"
